thread.title_full: Target says SEC doesn't plan to bring charges over data breach - MarketWatch

author: Steve Goldstein
title: Target says SEC doesn't plan to bring charges over data breach
text: The Securities and Exchange Commission's enforcement division does not plan to bring charges against Target TGT, -1.78% over its 2013 data breach. The retailer disclosed the SEC's intentions in a 10-Q filing . Target is still facing private litigation as well as investigations from states attorneys general and the Federal Trade Commission.
